OL,3,CPeanut allergy sufferers told to avoid
OL,4,Cmustard after contamination scare
OL,6,FThe agency is urgently working with
OL,7,Fthe relevant local authorities,
OL,8,Findividual businesses and industry to
OL,9,Fidentify which products may be
OL,10,Faffected.
OL,12,F"We have traced the contaminated
OL,13,Fmustard ingredients to a producer in
OL,14,FIndia called GT Agro Industries and
OL,15,Fhave identified one company who has
OL,16,Fsupplied these ingredients for use in
OL,17,FUK food," the FSA said.
