OL,6,F"If there is a risk that mustard could
OL,7,Fbe unintentionally present in food
OL,8,Fthere will be a 'may contain' label
OL,9,Ffor mustard.
OL,11,F"If you are eating out, please ask the
OL,12,Fcafe or restaurant staff if any of
OL,13,Ftheir products contain mustard ` by
OL,14,Flaw, food businesses must provide this
OL,15,Finformation to customers."
